GeneralComments:
Qualitician is considered as the leading job platform for software testing and quality assurance professionals. Our platform helps job seekers in finding manual and automation testing jobs, software testing walkins and software testing internships in India. For more details, visit our website now!
Qualitician aims to supply competent and successful software testing and quality assurance professionals to the organizations that need them. We are a technology company focused on helping employers find and hire talented Software Testing and QA Professionals. We provide customized recruitment process outsourcing solutions to our clients. Our team takes responsibilities of HR of all our clients such as resume management, screening candidates, interview scheduling, etc. for software testing and QA positions. Also, we are allowing registered organizations to list their software testing courses on our website.
